Package: mcreplicate
Description: Multi-core replication to make Monte Carlo simulation
  faster more easily. Based on the mcreplicate function from the rethinking
  package. The rethinking package requires installing rstan, which can be a 
  hurdle, while also not adding capabilities to this function.
Title: Multi-Core Replicate
Version: 0.1.0
